### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3003
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get all subject groups
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/subject-groups
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a new subject group (Customer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/subject-groups
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "KH_VIP",
  "name": "Khách VIP",
  "type": "customer",
  "description": "Nhóm khách hàng VIP"
}

### Create a new subject group (Vendor)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/subject-groups
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "NCC_TRONG_NUOC",
  "name": "NCC Trong Nước",
  "type": "vendor",
  "description": "Nhà cung cấp trong nước"
}

### Create a new subject group (Both)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/subject-groups
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "DOI_TAC_CHIEN_LUOC",
  "name": "Đối tác chiến lược",
  "type": "both",
  "description": "Đối tác quan trọng"
}
